    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Stanford researchers applied machine learning and deep learning techniques with deep neural networks through multi-layer architectures. Stanford researchers have applied One-Shot learning paradigm with long short-term memory on TensorFlow with DeepChem library. GlaxoSmithKline has agreed to share clinical trial data with chemical compounds and toxicology big data for a period of 15 years. GlaxoSmithKline is expected to revolutionize the drug discovery in the next few years with supercomputing and deep learning.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
